# API base for the dashboard.
#
# Leave EMPTY in production: the dashboard calls its same-origin Pages BFF
# (functions/), which Cloudflare Access protects and which forwards to the Worker
# with the BFF shared secret. The browser never talks to the Worker directly.
#
# Set this to the Worker URL only for local dev WITHOUT the BFF — but note the
# Worker now requires the BFF secret, so prefer `wrangler pages dev dist` (which
# runs the functions locally) over `vite dev` against the live Worker.
VITE_API_BASE=
